{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_xpe1gxusw262l5jfr2pqe","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"597439403","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/work/caveman-docs-from-code-1/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nIn-memory cache implementation using JavaScript Map.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance. Returns an object with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\nExample:\n\n```js\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key.\n\n- **Arguments**: `key` (string)\n- **Returns**: Value if found, `undefined` otherwise\n\n```js\nconst value = cache.get('my-key')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache.\n\n- **Arguments**:\n  - `key` (string) - Cache key\n  - `value` (any) - Value to store\n- **Returns**: The stored value\n\n```js\ncache.set('my-key', 'my-value')\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a key-value pair from the cache.\n\n- **Arguments**: `key` (string)\n- **Returns**: `true` if key existed and was deleted, `false` otherwise\n\n```js\nconst deleted = cache.delete('my-key')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5852,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":5740},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"68611247-8ed3-4fb0-aafb-6460aac50c70","uuid":"dadd67d8-1741-442c-987e-f2b0617b8246","timestamp":"2026-07-23T00:01:16.325Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"597439403","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /work/caveman-docs-from-code-1/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md (file state is current in your context — no need to Read it back)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"68611247-8ed3-4fb0-aafb-6460aac50c70","uuid":"5d0eb8a0-ff31-47d5-a426-acd035a0ef1a","timestamp":"2026-07-23T00:01:16.341Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/work/caveman-docs-from-code-1/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nIn-memory cache implementation using JavaScript Map.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance. Returns an object with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\nExample:\n\n```js\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key.\n\n- **Arguments**: `key` (string)\n- **Returns**: Value if found, `undefined` otherwise\n\n```js\nconst value = cache.get('my-key')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache.\n\n- **Arguments**:\n  - `key` (string) - Cache key\n  - `value` (any) - Value to store\n- **Returns**: The stored value\n\n```js\ncache.set('my-key', 'my-value')\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a key-value pair from the cache.\n\n- **Arguments**: `key` (string)\n- **Returns**: `true` if key existed and was deleted, `false` otherwise\n\n```js\nconst deleted = cache.delete('my-key')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
